| SAP Field          | FinSight Field | Data Type | Required | Transformation | Validation  |
| ------------------ | -------------- | --------- | -------- | -------------- | ----------- |
| Sales Order        | salesOrder     | String    | Yes      | Direct         | Unique      |
| Customer           | customerName   | String    | Yes      | Trim           | Mandatory   |
| Company Code       | companyCode    | String    | Yes      | Direct         | Exists      |
| Order Date         | orderDate      | Date      | Yes      | YYYY-MM-DD     | Valid Date  |
| Currency           | currency       | String    | Yes      | ISO 4217       | Currency    |
| Order Amount       | amount         | Decimal   | Yes      | Round(2)       | Positive    |
| Status             | status         | String    | Yes      | Uppercase      | OPEN/CLOSED |
| Sales Organization | salesOrg       | String    | Yes      | Direct         | Exists      |
